Text: Steve I know that these are trying times for you Just wanted to let you know that I am pulling for you in these difficult times If there is anything that I can do to help you please let me know You encouragement and support meant so much to me this past summer that I just had to send you this quick note of support Sincerely Yours Bob Lane Do You Yahoo Yahoo GeoCities quick and easy web site hosting just month psinfo
